text: Anna Zatuşevscaia (born 12 March 1995) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Moldova women's national team. ==Career== Zatuşevscaia has been capped for the Moldova national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
